  "about": [
    "The company logo, an \"X\" formed by a tiny arthroscope and a grasper, was originally sketched by Schmieding.",
    "While notoriously press-shy, the founder likes to keep his legacy intact; he's kept his $50 drafting table where he drafted his first operating instruments."
